## Priority Guide

| Priority | Meaning | When Claude Should Act |
|----------|---------|------------------------|
| **P0** | Urgent | Immediately, before other work |
| **P1** | Important | This session if time permits |
| **P2** | Normal | When relevant work is happening |
| **P3** | Low | When nothing else is pending |

